sequenceDiagram
    participant HB as 心跳定时器
    participant A as Agent
    participant T as TaskPilot CLI
    participant U as 用户

    HB->>A: 30分钟心跳
    A->>T: taskpilot heartbeat
    T-->>A: awareness JSON
    alt mood=chill
        A->>A: 静默
    else mood=gentle_push
        A->>U: 温和提醒
    else mood=urgent
        A->>U: 紧急提醒
    end
